# The scripts directory holds inspect / dev / one-off tooling the image
# doesn't need — exclude it to keep the build context small. The exception is
# the bundled migrate entrypoint: the builder stage runs `npx esbuild` over it
# to inline it into a self-contained `.cjs`, so that file (and its `lib/`
# imports) must reach the build context. Keep this negation in lockstep with the
# Dockerfile's esbuild step. The database bootstrap helper is also imported by
# the checked-in privilege-convergence integration test, which production
# type-checking sees even though the bootstrap CLI itself is not image runtime
# code.
scripts
!scripts/migrate.ts
!scripts/infra/databaseOwnerBootstrap.ts
